---
import PopupButton from "../../react-components/PopupButton";
---

<div class="hero">
    <div class="hero-top">
        <h3>Impulsa tu presencia en redes sociales con los servicios expertos de Conectividad Global</h3>
        <p>
            En Conectividad Global, comprendemos la importancia de las redes sociales en el panorama empresarial actual. Es por eso que nuestro equipo de especialistas te proporciona las herramientas necesarias para destacar en el mundo digital.
        </p>
        <PopupButton client:visible/>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-bottom">
        <div class="hero-bottom-left">
            <div class="hero-bottom-img">

            </div>
            <div class="hero-bottom-title">
                <h3>34+</h3>
                <p>AÃ±os de Experiencia</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-bottom-center">
            <div class="hero-bottom-img">

            </div>
            <div class="hero-bottom-title">
                <h3>68M</h3>
                <p>Seguidores en Redes</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="hero-bottom-right">
            <div class="hero-bottom-img">

            </div>
            <div class="hero-bottom-title">
                <h3>97%</h3>
                <p>Projectos Exitosos</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<style>
    .hero
    {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        padding: 5px 100px;
        gap: 30px;
    }

    .hero-top
    {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 20px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-top h3
    {
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero-top p
    {
        width: 90%;
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 200;
        color: #818181;
    }

    .hero-bottom
    {
        width: 100%;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 25px;
    }

    .hero-bottom-left,
    .hero-bottom-right
    {
        flex-basis: 35%;
    }

    .hero-bottom-center
    {
        flex-basis: 60%;
    }

    .hero-bottom-img
    {
        height: 275%;
        position: relative;
        border-radius: 30px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 20px;
        background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
        color: #FFF;
        overflow: hidden;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .hero-bottom-img::before
    {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: 0;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background-image: url("https://i.imgur.com/yfIBb7m.jpeg");
        background-size: cover;
        background-position: center;
        background-repeat: no-repeat;
        opacity: 1;
        z-index: -1;
        border-radius: 30px;
    }

    .hero-bottom-title
    {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 10px;
    }

    .hero-bottom-title h3
    {
        font-size: 40px;
        font-weight: 700;
    }

    .hero-bottom-title p
    {
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 200;
        color: #818181;
    }

    @media screen and (max-width: 768px)
    {
        .hero
        {
            padding: 25px 10px;
            height: 100%;
        }

        .hero-top h3
        {
            font-size: 30px;
        }

        .hero-top p
        {
            font-size: 12px;
        }

        .hero-bottom
        {
            height: 100%;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .hero-bottom-img
        {
            height: 100%;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        .hero-bottom-title h3
        {
            font-size: 32px;
        }

        .hero-bottom-title p
        {
            font-size: 14px;
        }
    }
</style>